Package crops

Custom crop object logic and structure created for Farm Simulator game

Contains the structure for a crop object and the unique constructors for the crop subclasses.
Crop extends FarmItem and all others extend Crop.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Alex Burling(arb142)
See Also:
Crop, Cactus, Melon, Mushroom, Pumpkin, SugarCane, Wheat
